"SCROLL OF BALL LIGHTNING\\nAllows user to cast \"Ball of Lightning"
"\"\\nAllows user to copy \"Ball of Lightning\" into Spell Book\\nLevel: 3 / "
"Wizard\\nRange: 90 ft. + 30 ft. per level\\nDuration: Instant\\nSpeed: "
"3\\nArea of Effect: Nearest target\\nSaving Throw: 1/2\\nWeight: 0\\nUsable "
"only by Mages\\n\\nSpheres of electrical force shoot forth and strike your "
"nearest foes. \\n\\nCaster can create up to 4 glowing spheres of lightning "
"when the spell is cast. They are roughly 3 ft. in diameter. The damage "
"varies depending on the number of balls created:\\n\\n4        2d4 each"
"\\n3        2d6 each\\n2        5d4 each\\n1        4d12"
